Chicago Branch  2
A,3:Add two advancement counters to an installed card that can be
advanced.

There has been a great deal of discussion on this list about corp speed
decks.  This particular card does not seem to have had a look in.  O.K it
is easy to trash (1) and is more expensive than say Systematic Layoffs,
but if you can defend it and get some bit creation going then you can
zoom though your agendas with this baby.
Agree?  Disagree?

P.S any players from u.k on this list, Leicestershire pref.  Mail me.

