> must play JoA/MFS.  If you play anything less than these, you will
> loose decisively.

  You mean I must throw away all of my other decks, because they won by
   chance?

> Anyway, my original predictions for the game are still on track.  The
> game has turned into a battle of degenerate and not-very-fun decks.
> In six months (five now) it will dwindle down to just the hard-core
> players with degenerate decks who can't find anyone (except other
> degenerate decks) to play (much like what happened to Star Trek,
> Star Wars, INWO, etc.).
