From:         Michael Blumoehr <michael@IEZ.COM>
Subject:      Setup & Speed Trap

Hello,
first I want to thank you for the contributions to this list. I am reading
it for 2 weeks and get lot of hints and a lot more of fun from hit. Please
go on.

Second I have a question. (I've played only 5 games of NR yet.) Yesterday we
had the following situation. Runner has installed

Speed Trap
Program-Detection-1 MU
[0]: Jack out before an upgrade or node takes effect. Use this ability only
immediately after the Corp has rezzed that upgrade or node.

and made a run on HQ. He accessed:

Setup!
Node-Ambush
When Runner accesses Setup!, it does 2 Net damage, even if it is not
installed. Ignore this effect if Runner accesses it from the Archives. If
Setup! is accessed from R&D, Runner must show it to you.

The question: Must the runner take the damage or not?
We decided he must take the damage. The Setup is not installed and it
states, 'does 2 Net damage, even it is not installed'. I read this as, I
need not to rez Setup to do the damage (and I can't rez a node in HQ too).
Speed Trap allows to jack out only after the Corp has rezzed that upgrade.
Result: He cannot jack out and has to take the damage.

Michael.
-----------------------------------
Michael Blumoehr
michael@iez.com
