> seems frustrating that WotC would release a new game that is an obvious
> breeding pit for degenerateness.

"Degenerate is as degenerate does."

We *still* haven't seen this combination dominate tournament play, nor
have we received feedback stating that it's being done at non-WotC events.

I asked for first-hand accounts a week ago, and haven't received any yet.
Just a lot of complaints about it with no backing, as well as a lot of
'solutions' to something that hasn't been proven to be a problem.

The next rules team meeting is on Wednesday.  I'd really like to have
some information to share there....

