Subject:      Runner always wins?

I have been playing Netrunner for a while now. Myself and a friend play
mostly in pairs of games, swapping sides.

Well for quite some time only the corp has been winning. But last night we
played 4 games and the runner won every one. In one game the corp didn't
even score a single agenda!

I think this was because since the runner was always losing we have been
only working on the runner decks and not at all on the corp decks. Now we
will have to start work on the corp decks!

So, I my opinion, the corp does have an advantage but an experienced runner
(with a good deck) can tip the balance the other way.



