(103 including sideboard) and made of Zombies and some support. Everyone
looks at it and says it cant win so I offer to play them in Ante I crush
them they dont understand. I have played this deck for 2+ years and have
an 81% win ratio people still say it cant win it does why because I
understand How to play the deck If I switch decks with them I usually
win again with their deck "HMM" they say, "see it cant win you must just
have been lucky." but they wont play it again in ANTE. Maybe we should
start playing NR with an ANTE system see if you want to back up your
JOA/MFS combo. (by the way I do play ANTE NR you ante UP a card from
each of your decks one at the start of each round the winner by points
takes both cards)
