  You can get at least 1 bit 50% of the time from this card if you always
take 1 bit from each die.  So on a 1 take 1 bit, on a 2 take 1 bit and 1
roll, and on a 3 take 1 bit and 2 rolls.  The most my computer got at 1
time was 37 bits ( this was on a trial run of 10,000 ).

