3) They tend to run out of bits, so I can walk any trace routines for
free.
4) Any 'Insta-Trace' card requires the corp to spend a minimum of 2 bits
extra just to find me.
5) I can't be chance observed/U renewal on the second turn (hasn't
happened yet) when I play this card first.

6*) Great flavor text.  Just imagine a bloodthirsty slobbering cerebus
trying to gain access to a College 'Virtual Classroom' and being stopped
by the pedantic school administration.  Totally cool.

