Subject:      Re: Peeking at Trash/Archives

Blue Dragon wrote:
> Can the Corp look through the Runner's Trash pile at any time?

Yes.

> Can the Runner look through the Corp's faceup Archives at any time
> or only after a successful Archives run?

Any time, but face-up only (obviously).

> The latter case came up recently when the Corp used Off-Site Backups
> to grab a card out of Archives, and I wanted to check Archives to
> see which card had disappeared.

Since you can do this, it's usually polite to simply show your opponent
the card you take when you go through your trash or archives.  At least
in friendly games....

