Looks great except for one thing...

Under 15, I believe that the corp should determine the order in which
upgrades are accessed.  Many upgrades are ambush upgrades, and the corp
can assume to be setting up a trap for the runner when they place these
upgrades.

I would also be quite happy if the corp was allowed to choose only the
order of ambush upgrades.

Seems fair, no?

