That's the silliest thing I've ever heard! Do you *really* play against
people with such horrible poker faces? I only play against one guy who does
that, and he mixes it up sometimes so that he winces when I'm about to grap
a Trap! or Setup!. In short, I can't trust his facial expressions. And
nobody else shows any. Personally, I always look amused when the runner is
waving his fingers over my HQ...
Smile. Runners will wonder what you're up to.

