I can vouch for the helpfulness of this route.  One of my friends owns
several thousand m:tg cards.  Not only does he trade and often loan, but
he also makes a practice of building decks for people and giving them to
them for free or cheaply.  Not only does it make him a bit of money, but
it also solves the problem of not having enough people to play with.

