start-up package and no Duelist #11.  I have spent almost as much in phone
calls as I did for my membership.

  This corp (DCI) uses a lot of specialized ICE :

1. The dreaded VOICE MAIL. (Press 1 now....Please leave a message for us to
ignore.)

2. THE CHECKS IN THE MAIL. (Oh, that is going out today [week 11].  Let me
know if you don't get it by next week.)

3. The ever popular WE DON'T HANDLE THAT HERE. (Please call 555-YOUR-SCREWED
for that.)

  I am very tired of being jacked out (around) by THE DUELIST CONVOCATION.
This it to them --- YOU HAVE MY MONEY...I WANT MY STUFF.  JUST HOW MANY BAD
PUBLICITY COUNTERS DOES IT TAKE TO KILL A CORP !!!???.  TWELVE WEEKS (12) IS
TOO LONG.  YOUR UNCARING ATTITUDE IS OFFENSIVE.  AT WORST YOU HAVE STOLLEN
MY MONEY.  AT BEST YOUR CUSTOMER SERVICE (for lack of a better word) SUCKS.

  To the rest of you I am sorry for the waste of your Netrunner space.  But
I would like to know it I am the only one getting screwed like this.

